# Copy to .env.local.
#
# The public OAuth client_id registered for this SPA (a PKCE public client —
# no secret, since the whole point of PKCE is that browser-based apps can't
# hold one safely). Create it once against the running server:
#   node scripts/create-client.mjs --name="WhiteBox UI" --redirect-uri=http://localhost:5173/callback
# (run from server-plugin-oauth/ — see its README) and paste the printed
# client_id below. No other env var is needed: every module authenticates
# with the logged-in user's own session token, not a shared static secret.
VITE_OAUTH_CLIENT_ID=
